{"tid":1785460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"省港盃保傳統暫緩舉行","createTime":"2019-12-16T11:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T11:38:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cb8907001b655715429598a2e2e3d88f8f174b","tid":1785460,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191213/TWZBVEWEF53B6FYIEPQO7UBTGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191213%2FTWZBVEWEF53B6FYIEPQO7UBTGE%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7vTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=125db3c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191213%2FTWZBVEWEF53B6FYIEPQO7UBTGE%2F&h=cb85f443\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191213/TWZBVEWEF53B6FYIEPQO7UBTGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n省港盃保傳統暫緩舉行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191213/large/1576164983_88bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191213%2Flarge%2F1576164983_88bc.jpg&h=17da2d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港足總宣佈今屆省港盃（圖）將會暫緩舉行。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】足總主席貝鈞奇昨晚在董事會後表示，廣東足協考慮到目前香港社會及環境，又希望保持省港盃的傳統，經協商後決定暫緩舉行今屆省港盃。<br />\n<br />\n第42屆省港盃原定下月中舉行，但一直未有確實賽期，早前國內有消息新一屆省港盃足球賽，因應香港目前局勢，可能由傳統的兩回合賽事，改為一回合決勝，賽事安排在廣東舉行；貝鈞奇當時未有正面回應，只謂不排除任何可能性。<br />\n<br />\n貝鈞奇在董事會後透露，與廣東體育總局及廣東足協溝通後，雙方認為需要保留省港盃在兩地進行兩回合賽事的傳統，故現時選擇先暫緩賽事，至於何時復賽，要視乎香港氣氛及局勢：「雖然香港近期社會相對比較平靜，但不希望出現任何情況，寧願再觀察多一段時間，故先暫緩賽事，至於暫緩到何時，要視乎情況。」<br />\n<br />\n今屆省港盃原定下月9及16日進行兩回合賽事，廣東隊已初步定出名單，並由曹陽任主教練領軍，以中甲梅州客家球員作為班底爭取重奪省港盃，不過，廣東對來港作賽是有所顧慮而導致賽事未能落實，最終暫緩。另外，原定九月底上演，由和富大埔對傑志的社區盃，因抗權運動而延期，暫未有補賽時間表。<br />\n<br />\n貝鈞奇謂，香港飛馬原先有意承辦明年一月底的賀歲盃，但最終決定退出，因時間比較緊迫，要邀請外隊來港作賽有困難，足總正留意是否有外隊探盤，最壞打算是再以港隊對港聯頂檔。<br />\n<br />\n記者：曾雁平"},{"pid":"a344c7b3a6e76a131dff53216eb853a9e24e2c5d","tid":1785460,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79361407_152866279456715_1551513620934819840_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQmAvyxgZu5T2VDaPtTOxDhzelZTE0Kn6aEMZ7R4p1do2OXZP_vbNkrmi7bn7Ml2AHk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=703c1ff8ccb8fc8cc77d959ea38cd7d7&amp;oe=5EB36A76\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79361407_152866279456715_1551513620934819840_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQmAvyxgZu5T2VDaPtTOxDhzelZTE0Kn6aEMZ7R4p1do2OXZP_vbNkrmi7bn7Ml2AHk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3D703c1ff8ccb8fc8cc77d959ea38cd7d7%26oe%3D5EB36A76&h=ca3dd940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn